| Node | Fields | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `SimilarPattern` | `text: str` | `similar("user wants a refund")` — text captured for compile-time embedding (Phase 3 reads this) |
| `WildcardPattern` | — | `_` |
| `ExprPattern` | `expr: Expr` | Fallback for any other expression-as-pattern (literal match) |

