# Phase 04 Plan 05: Agents, Tools, Prompts, Classes Summary

GEN-01 construct coverage for agents, tools, prompts, classes, spawn, and gather is implemented and covered by focused codegen tests.

## Tasks

| Task | Status | Notes |
