    1. `pub async fn read_frame<R: tokio::io::AsyncBufRead + Unpin>(r: &mut R) -> std::io::Result<Vec<u8>>` that:
       - Loops reading lines via `r.read_line(&mut buf).await` until it sees an empty `\r\n` (header terminator).
